  <md:title>What Is Social Stratification?</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you should be able to:</para><list>
<item>Differentiate between open and closed stratification systems</item>
<item>Distinguish between caste and class systems</item>
<item>Explain why meritocracy is considered an ideal system of stratification</item>
</list></md:abstract>
